{"tid":2297330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZONE確定12月7日回歸 新專主題為“青春·成長”","createTime":"2020-11-23T07:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T17:56:41.000Z","uid":251328,"like":11,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"04f2e4842a6d2b530f36cadef990b00ec4e9c164","tid":2297330,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"韓國人氣女團IZONE將時隔6個月回歸，12月7日確定發行新專。<br />\n<br />\n23日，IZONE通過官方SNS公開了包含新專發售信息的回歸預告海報。公開的海報中記載了專輯名《One-reeler》和回歸時間&ldquo;2020 DECEMBER 07 MONDAY 6PM&rdquo;。該專輯是IZONE繼6月發行的第三張迷你專輯《Oneiric Diary》以來時隔6個月推出的第四張迷你專輯。如專輯名&ldquo;One-reeler&rdquo;意為著短篇電影一樣，通過該專輯IZONE成員們將以電影中的某個場面的形式，用三個&ldquo;Scene&rdquo;展現青春和成長的故事。<br />\n<br />\n另外，該專輯將於12月7日下午3點（韓國時間）通過各個唱片網站進行預售。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8ox282.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8ox282.jpg&h=760efb28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d513b6001b6a86f974bb93ee2baa36c476ed139","tid":2297330,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20201123/0/3/58/IZONE確定12月7日回歸-新專主題為青春成長-12438012.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20201123%2F0%2F3%2F58%2FIZONE%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A12%E6%9C%887%E6%97%A5%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8-%E6%96%B0%E5%B0%88%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-12438012.html&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=98b26466\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20201123/0/3/58/IZONE確定12月7日回歸-新專主題為青春成長-12438012.html</a>"},{"pid":"95631b8561ccde50741a23d04e47d50bfe0a5ee2","tid":2297330,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:59:18.000Z","msg":"ONE REELER<br />\n大發<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"h